snippet.textDisplay:
Yes, Arsenal should've done better in the first thirty minutes of the game. There were too many sideways passes instead of pinging the ball to Ozil who was finding space between the lines. The one time he did get that pass he combined with Laca and Auba for the goal. This would've been a totally different game had we scored two or three during that opening period of dominance.


That said, Arsenal showed good character in getting the draw considering everything that happened during the final hour of the game. We should take that positive and the point and move on. COYG !!!
